[size=5][color=#ffff00][b]Credits[/b][/color][/size]
Most of the original set info came from [url=https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077_Cosmetic_Sets]Cyberpunk 2077 Cosmetic Sets[/url] and various fragmented sources on the internet. Much of which was out of date as of patch 2.0, so the locations and directions in this guide were validated and rewritten in-game.

